    <text>
        <group>
            <text type="letter" xml:lang="ru" xml:id="letter-01113">
                <body>
                    <opener>
                        <salute rend="inline">
                            <persName ref="people.xml#pan01">Никита Иванович!</persName>
                        </salute>
                    </opener>
                    <p>Письмо Ваше и при оном пакет мною получен. Я весьма радуюсь, слыша, что
                            <persName ref="people.xml#pot01">Великой Князь</persName> в добром
                        здоровье находится, и то же самое известие о себе Вам даю, пребывая всегда
                        доброжелательною.</p>
                    <closer>
                        <signed>
                            <persName ref="people.xml#cat01">Екатерина.</persName>
                        </signed>
                        <dateline>
                            <placeName ref="places.xml#tsa01">С. Сарское.</placeName>
                            <lb/>
                            <date when-custom="1764-01-25">25 Генваря, 1764 г.</date>
                        </dateline>
                    </closer>
                </body>
            </text>
            <text type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <body><opener><salute rend="inline"><persName ref="people.xml#pan01">Nikita
                                Ivanovich!</persName></salute></opener><p>Your letter and the
                        accompanying packet have been received by me. I am very glad to hear that
                        the <persName ref="people.xml#pot01">Grand Duke</persName> is in good
                    health, and I send you the same news about myself, remaining always your
                                well-wisher.</p><closer><signed><persName ref="people.xml#cat01"
                                >Catherine.</persName></signed><dateline><placeName
                                ref="places.xml#tsa01">S. Tsarskoe.</placeName><lb/><date
                                when-custom="1764-01-25">25 January,
                    1764</date></dateline></closer></body>
            </text>
        </group>
    </text>
